    "content": "<p>What's behind door number one? Or how about door number two? Players of Montezuma's Treasure can find out in the Bonus game, where they'll encounter a screen with a door in the center and five different objects to choose from. Will it be a prize? Or maybe passage to the next level? The anticipation is real.</p><p>But beware, with great rewards come great risks. Players have up to three, five, or even seven lives. Lose too many, and you're out like a certain Australian marsupial.</p>"
}

